headline: Walgreens Boots Alliance Schedules Fiscal 2025 First Quarter Earnings Announcement for January 9
summary: DEERFIELD, Ill., December 06, 2024--Walgreens Boots Alliance, Inc. (Nasdaq: WBA) will release its fiscal year 2025 first quarter results at 7 a.m. ET on Thursday, January 9, followed by a one-hour conference call with WBA management beginning at 8:30 a.m. ET.
